I’ve identified the likely gap: when cue counts are empty, family ranking currently returns nothing, so `hybrid->frame` adaptive ambiguity never surfaces at compile time. I’m adding a deterministic logit-softmax fallback ranking for adaptive ambiguity only, plus a priority-policy tweak and focused tests.
